name: Pipeline Brickell
overview:
Pipeline Brickell exists for one fundamental reason: to provide an extraordinary environment for people and businesses to unleash their ideas, passions, and creativity.

Pipeline is a high design shared workspace used by a diverse community of entrepreneurs, startups, independent professionals and small business teams. Unique from other shared workspaces, Pipeline is a purpose-built environment that provides members a variety of areas to focus, collaborate, learn or socialize at any given time. By reimagining the traditional workspace, Pipeline gives our members the greatest opportunities for productivity and success.
